Package: qemu-rpi-system-arm
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
 qemu-rpi-system-data (= ${source:Version}),
Description: QEMU with Raspberry Pi 4B GENET Ethernet support
 Modified QEMU emulator for ARM systems with BCM2838 GENET Ethernet
 controller support for Raspberry Pi 4 Model B emulation.
 .
 This package provides qemu-rpi-system-aarch64, which can be installed
 alongside the standard Debian qemu-system-arm package.
 .
 Includes: GENET Ethernet (1Gbps), PCIe Root Complex, RNG200, Thermal.

Package: qemu-rpi-system-data
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: QEMU RPi data files (firmware, keymaps, etc.)
 Data files needed by qemu-rpi-system-arm.
 .
 Contains firmware blobs, keymaps, and other architecture-independent
 files for the QEMU RPi build.
